msgstr "But then strong winds carved up my belly, "

msgctxt "mn100:21.5"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, bhāradvāja, dakkho goghātako vā goghātakantevāsī vā tiṇhena govikantanena kucchiṃ parikanteyya; "
msgstr "like a deft butcher or their apprentice was slicing my belly open with a meat cleaver. "

msgctxt "mn100:21.6"
msgid "evameva kho me, bhāradvāja, mukhato ca nāsato ca kaṇṇato ca assāsapassāsesu uparuddhesu adhimattā vātā kucchiṃ parikantanti. "
